channel.title: Hello.. may I please get some help please?
channel.description:
Well I got this error and I'm trying to not make myself look like a fool like those other moparscaper people, but can you please help me with this error? When I downloaded silabsofts client I got this error,and I got an error that's this and I have no idea what it is.
[code] C:\Documents and Settings\Compaq_Owner\My Documents\my games>JAVA -Xmx500m -jar client.jar 0 0 highmem members 0 Exception in thread "main" java.lang.UnsupportedClassVersionError: client (Unsup ported major.minor version 49.0) at java.lang.ClassLoader.defineClass0(Native Method) at java.lang.ClassLoader.defineClass(Unknown Source) at java.security.SecureClassLoader.defineClass(Unknown Source) at java.net.URLClassLoader.defineClass(Unknown Source) at java.net.URLClassLoader.access$100(Unknown Source) at java.net.URLClassLoader$1.run(Unknown Source) at java.security.AccessController.doPrivileged(Native Method) at java.net.URLClassLoader.findClass(Unknown Source) at java.lang.ClassLoader.loadClass(Unknown Source) at sun.misc.Launcher$AppClassLoader.loadClass(Unknown Source) at java.lang.ClassLoader.loadClass(Unknown Source) at java.lang.ClassLoader.loadClassInternal(Unknown Source)
C:\Documents and Settings\Compaq_Owner\My Documents\my games>pause Press any key to continue . . .[/code]
